Text: WATCH and laugh: possibly the BEST vine of Hillary from the 2016 campaign … so far Posted at 4:23 pm on October 27, 2016 by Sam J.   Several weeks back, Twitter was hee-haw’ing over the short “vine” of Hillary saying over and over and over again, “Why am I not 50 points ahead?!”   This vine takes it one step further, and the payoff is awesome.   — Andrew Kugle (@AndrewJKugle) October 27, 2016   You’ve got this thing set to evil.
